## App interface

App represents a set of publishing data and configuration data for running the app.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export interface App extends Localizable<LocaleSpecificApp> 
```
<b>Extends:</b> [Localizable](./stentor-models.localizable.md)<!-- -->&lt;[LocaleSpecificApp](./stentor-models.localespecificapp.md)<!-- -->&gt;
